{
  "stem": "142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, they give you all the tools, you know, what they had to-- all the tools to-- you know, every 20 minutes, you have to turn them around, you know, with-- with every two hours, you know-- it takes 30-- 30, 40 minutes to burn 'em.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was a-- there they had some false showers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were a few openings where the-- the Zyklon B, you know, was thrown from the SS.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of the chamber, I told you, that maybe will take 400, 500 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to put 2,500 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the doors were automatically closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- the doors were like the-- the butcher, this, you know, the very, very good, good doors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a big-- where you can see-- you-- they were coming from Berlin most of the time, and seeing how the Jews were dying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, also, you know, at that time, were also bunkers, not only crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where during the transports of the-- of Hungary, you know, there were-- we were working about two, three shifts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- the crematorium couldn't burn enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they had 2,000, 3,000 bunkers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were a lot of SS girls, laughing and laughing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- I couldn't see how a human being could do such a thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From time to time-- from time to time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were tell them, you know, just in-- in a very few words, you know, that they are going to die.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were bringing in-- you know-- they-- they thought that they are coming to-- we were very-- very well nourished, because all the food they were bringing in, we were eating it, actually.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
